The following is a checklist to be followed for releasing new versions
of PTPd.

*) Make sure that your svn is up to date (svn update)

*) Build on FreeBSD

*) Build on Linux

*) Build on MacOS

*) Check startup.c and ptpd.c for any changes to default options.

*) Make sure that the manual page (ptpdX.8) matches the code.

*) Create a release tag (svn cp)

*) Update to the release tag

*) Build for FreeBSD

*) Build for Linux

*) Build for Mac OS
